'''''Video Trek 88''''' is a computer game developed and published by [[Windmill Software]] in 1982, based on the earlier ''[[Star Trek (1971 video game)|Star Trek]]'' text game. As opposed to the mainframe version, both the galactic chart and the local map are displayed side by side.

[[File:Video Trek 88.png|thumb|A game in progress]]
